stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle

    Idle --> EnteringData : Start Transaction Entry
    EnteringData --> Validating : Submit Transaction

    Validating --> Error : Validation Failed
    Error --> EnteringData : Correct Input

    Validating --> Saving : Validation Successful
    Saving --> Stored : Data Persisted

    Stored --> UpdatingUI : Refresh Dashboard
    UpdatingUI --> Idle : Complete